lass=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_5\">la mentira a la sinceridad.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.52.6\" class=\"v19_52_6\">6<\/sup>Amas la palabra que destruye<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_6\">y es enga\u00f1osa tu lengua.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.52.7\" class=\"v19_52_7\">7<\/sup>Dios te aniquilar\u00e1 para siempre,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_7\">te expulsar\u00e1, te sacar\u00e1 de tu tienda,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_7\">te arrancar\u00e1 de la tierra de los vivos. [<span class=\"it\">Pausa<\/span>]<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.52.8\" class=\"v19_52_8\">8<\/sup>Y los justos lo ver\u00e1n asustados<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_8\">y empezar\u00e1n a re\u00edrse de \u00e9l:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.52.9\" class=\"v19_52_9\">9<\/sup>\u201cMira, esta es la persona<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_9\">que no hizo de Dios su fortaleza,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_9\">que confi\u00f3 en su inmensa riqueza,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_9\">que se refugi\u00f3 en su maldad.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_10\"><sup id=\"Ps.52.10\" class=\"v19_52_10\">10<\/sup>Pero yo soy frondoso olivo<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_10\">en la morada de Dios<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_10\">y por siempre jam\u00e1s<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_10\">conf\u00edo en su amor.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_11\"><sup id=\"Ps.52.11\" class=\"v19_52_11\">11<\/sup>Yo siempre te alabar\u00e9<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_11\">por lo que has hecho<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_11\">y proclamar\u00e9 tu buen nombre<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_52_11\">ante los que te son fieles.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"52","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.52","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.52.11","order":"19052","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/52","display":"SALMOS 52","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n hispanoamericana Copyright &#169; Sociedad B&#237;blica de Espa&#241;a, 2011 Utilizada con permiso<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/sociedadbiblica.org","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.51","nextChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.53","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]}